data.name: ratna sari dewi
data.title: Victory in the Victory. I'll see you in Adelaide

videoDescription.value:
Since I know the sense of adventure, my life without adventure like cooking without salt. 
Since 10 years ago, I wanted an adventure to Adelaide, but I have not enough money. And finally, this Grand Prize into a christmas gift and special birthday present for me because the exact date of January 15, I got older. 
Thank you for Air Asia, Adelaide, Lonely Planet and all my friends for your support so I selected as miss adventure 2014. I will see you in Adelaide.

Kangaroo Island could be a distillation Australia's natural wonders, which makes every corner of it breathtaking. To experience it would be one of life's cornerstone moments, which is why my hope is AirAsia can spread its awesomeness for me to soak it up in person.

Hi Air Asia X,
Pick me to go to Kangaroo Island, Adelaide!
